# SOC Framework + CSOC JIRA Configuration Integration

## Overview

This document bridges the **SOC Framework v1.0** (7 analytics, 10 use cases, 8 automation rules) with your **detailed CSOC JIRA Configuration Guide** (100+ use cases, custom fields, workflows, Confluence integration).

---

## How They Work Together

### The Framework Provides:
- **Foundation**: 7 core analytics + 10 core use cases
- **Architecture**: Data flow, integration patterns, JIRA automation
- **Quick Start**: 30-day deployment roadmap
- **Playbooks**: Detailed UC-001 example + response procedures

### CSOC Guide Provides:
- **Depth**: 100+ use cases across all attack categories
- **Configuration Details**: Exact JIRA field definitions and workflows
- **Data Sources**: Comprehensive Windows Event and Sysmon mapping
- **Confluence Structure**: Shadow documentation and knowledge management
- **Best Practices**: Handling legacy systems, undocumented assets, policy violations

---

