### Phase 2: Implement CSOC Configuration (Weeks 3-8)
**Expand with detailed CSOC fields, workflows, and 100+ use cases**

#### Step 1: Add CSOC Custom Fields (Week 3)

**From CSOC Guide - Core Alert/Incident Fields:**
```
Add to JIRA:
â”œâ”€ Alert Rule Name (already have)
â”œâ”€ Alert Source (Select: Search Head, SIEM, SOAR, Manual)
â”œâ”€ Detection Query (Text Long - store full SPL)
â”œâ”€ Search Head Link (URL - back to Splunk)
â”œâ”€ First Seen / Last Seen (DateTime)
â”œâ”€ Event Count (Number)
â”œâ”€ Confidence Score (Low/Medium/High)
â””â”€ Alert Disposition (9 values from CSOC guide)
```

**Add CSOC MITRE ATT&CK Fields:**
```
â”œâ”€ ATT&CK Tactic (Multi-Select)
â”œâ”€ ATT&CK Technique (Cascading)
