**Total Custom Fields Added:** ~28 fields
**Estimated JIRA Configuration Time:** 4-6 hours

#### Step 2: Update JIRA Workflows (Week 3)

**Replace simple Framework workflow with CSOC workflows:**

**Replace:**
```
Simple: Triage â†’ Investigation â†’ Containment â†’ Eradication â†’ Recovery â†’ Closed
```

**With CSOC Structure:**
```
Security Alert Workflow:
New Alert â†’ Triage â†’ Change Validation (or Investigating) â†’ Resolved â†’ Closed

Security Incident Workflow (promoted):
Identification â†’ Containment â†’ Eradication â†’ Recovery â†’ Lessons Learned â†’ Closed

Policy Violation Workflow:
Policy Violation â†’ Pending Review â†’ Escalated â†’ Resolved â†’ Closed
```

**Estimated Time:** 4-6 hours

