**Content Development:**
- Week 4: UC-001 through UC-025 (25 use cases)
- Week 5: UC-026 through UC-050 (25 use cases)
- Week 6: UC-051 through UC-075 (25 use cases)
- Week 7: UC-076 through UC-104 (29 use cases)
- Week 8: Polish, cross-reference, validate completeness

**Estimated Time:** 2-3 hours per use case Ã— 100 = 200-300 hours over 4 weeks (can be distributed across team)

#### Step 4: Implement Advanced Automation Rules (Week 5-6)

**Framework provided 8 basic rules. Add CSOC enhancements:**

```
From Framework (keep as-is):
1. Alert Ingestion & Enrichment
2. Use Case & RE&CT Mapping
3. Assignment & SLA Configuration
4. RE&CT Phase Progression
5. Evidence Collection Automation
6. Escalation Logic
7. Notification & Communication
8. Verdict & Closure

Add CSOC Advanced Rules:
9. Auto-populate ATT&CK from Use Case
10. Change Ticket Validation Reminder
11. Auto-link Related Alerts
12. Promote to Incident (Issue Type Conversion)
13. Documentation Enforcement
14. Baseline Learning (FP categorization)
15. Asset Documentation Update
16. Policy Violation Detection
17. Undocumented System Alert
```

**Estimated Time:** 2-3 hours per rule Ã— 8 new rules = 16-24 hours

