## Mapping Framework to CSOC Details

### Analytics Mapping

**Framework provides 7 core analytics. CSOC guide provides 104 use cases.**

```
Framework Analytic â†’ CSOC Use Cases

ANALYTIC-001: Admin Group Addition â†’ UC-001, UC-002, UC-003, UC-011 through UC-017
ANALYTIC-002: Suspicious Process â†’ UC-035 through UC-045, UC-060 through UC-066
ANALYTIC-003: Failed Login Spike â†’ UC-018 through UC-025 (brute force)
ANALYTIC-004: LSASS Access â†’ UC-018 through UC-025 (credential access)
ANALYTIC-005: Lateral Movement â†’ UC-046 through UC-053
ANALYTIC-006: Data Exfiltration â†’ UC-054 through UC-059
ANALYTIC-007: Privilege Escalation â†’ UC-026 through UC-034, UC-060 through UC-066
```

**Example: ANALYTIC-004 Expansion**

Framework provides UC-004 (OS Credential Dumping - LSASS Access)

CSOC guide expands with:
- UC-018: LSASS Memory Access (from CSOC guide)
- UC-019: Credential Dumping Tool Keywords (from CSOC guide)
- Plus UC-020 through UC-025 for other credential access techniques

