## Custom Field Implementation Timeline

### Week 1-2 (Framework Phase)
**Minimal fields needed:**
- Use-Case
- MITRE-ATT&CK
- Severity
- RE&CT-Phase
- Playbook-Link
- SLA-Response
- SLA-Resolution

### Week 3 (CSOC Integration)
**Add comprehensive fields all at once:**
```
Total fields to add: ~28
â”Œâ”€ Alert/Incident Core (10 fields)
â”œâ”€ MITRE ATT&CK (4 fields)
â”œâ”€ RE&CT Framework (2 fields)
â”œâ”€ Affected Assets (6 fields)
â”œâ”€ Change Management (3 fields)
â””â”€ Investigation (3 fields)
```

**Implementation approach:**
1. Create all fields in dev JIRA
2. Test with 10-20 sample alerts
3. Train analysts on new fields
4. Deploy to production
5. Update all existing alerts (backfill)

**Backfill Strategy:**
- Prioritize CRITICAL and HIGH severity alerts
- Use bulk edit where possible
- New alerts auto-populate from Splunk webhook

